<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.2.3">
<l>tiriyuṅ kaliyuka nīṅkit tēvarka ṭāmum pukuntu</l>
<l>periya kitayukam paṟṟip pēriṉpa veḷḷam peruka</l>
<l>kariya mukilvaṇṇa ṉemmāṉ kaṭalvaṇṇaṉ pūtaṅkaṇ maṇmēl</l>
<l>iriyap pukunticai pāṭi yeṅku miṭaṅkoṇ ṭaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Kaliyuga is turning, and while, as  the gods themselves leave [and] enter,</l>
<l>the flood of great joy about the great Kṛtayuga increases,</l>
<l>the bhūtas of the one the colour of a black cloud, our lord, the ocean-coloured one</l>
<l>enter on earth so as to recede, sing music [and] take room everywhere.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
